window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>ONE OF THE “FEW GREAT INVESTMENT BOOKS”* EVER WRITTEN.</p> <p>In a time of rampant misinformation about ways of growing your money, Burton G. Malkiel’s gimmick-free investment guide is more necessary than ever. In this fully updated edition, Malkiel reveals how to be a tax-smart investor and addresses current investment trends, including factor investing, risk parity, cryptocurrencies, and ESG portfolios. A Random Walk Down Wall Street remains the best investment guide money can buy.</p> <p>“A must-read for any investor.”—Browser</p> <p>* Andrew Tobias</p>"; 
